# Mobile-First UI Guidelines

## Touch Targets
- Minimum 44px height/width for all interactive elements
- 12px spacing between touch targets
- Use proper focus states for accessibility
## Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach with Tailwind CSS
- Test breakpoints: 320px (mobile), 768px (tablet), 1024px (desktop)
- Use responsive Tailwind classes (sm:, md:, lg:)

## React-Admin Customization
- Override Material-UI components with Tailwind classes
- Ensure all forms work well on mobile keyboards
- Implement proper loading states and error messages

